ENHANCED VERSION NOTICE:

This version includes significant enhancements for live-cell RNA structure analysis:
- Statistical denoising algorithms using Fisher's exact test and multiple testing correction
- Customizable nucleotide selection for mutation rate analysis
- Control-experimental comparison pipeline for proximity labeling data
- Improved clustering algorithms for low signal-to-noise ratio data

Enhanced features developed by:
Ziyuan Wang, ShuoHan Lab, CEMCS
Contact: wangziyuan2024@sibcb.ac.cn

Original DREEM method published in:
Tomezsko, P.J., Corbin, V.D.A., Gupta, P. et al. 
Determination of RNA structural diversity and its role in HIV-1 RNA splicing. 
Nature 582, 438â€“442 (2020).

Original code available at:
